"withdrawal_content" = "<b>Note<font color='red'>(required)</font></b><br/>
Please note that your <font color='red'>your account cannot be recovered once </font>the withdrawal is completed.<br/><br/>
App usage history (document history, NFC registration history, etc.) will be deleted when the withdrawal is completed and cannot be recovered.<br/><br/>
<b>How to withdraw from membership</b><br/>
To prevent illegal theft and disadvantages when withdrawing from membership, the smartphone authentication process which was used at membership signup is performed. After completing the smartphone authentication, the application for withdrawal of membership will be processed.<br/><br/>
<b>Waiting period for withdrawal of membership</b><br/>
There is a 14-day waiting period for withdrawal after completion of authentication, and you can cancel your withdrawal during the waiting period";

